          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer898331638" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14396929492596323225">What a long, winding, complicated road one must travel to come to the end of this journey. At worst it was very confusing, at best it was quite interesting. <br/>On the whole, it was just compelling enough, despite the fits of frustration, to keep me coming back - reading word by word until the very end. </span>

          </span>
